msgstr "MAC 位址"

msgid "Manage configured wake devices, inspect their current reachability, and trigger wake or shutdown actions without leaving the page."
msgstr "管理已設定的喚醒裝置，檢視目前可達性，並直接在此頁面執行喚醒或關機。"

msgid "Manual Operation"
msgstr "手動操作"

msgid "No IPv4 address available for shutdown target. Ensure the host is online or has a host hint entry."
msgstr "沒有可用於關機目標的 IPv4 位址。請確認主機在線上，或存在對應的主機提示記錄。"

msgid "No devices have been configured yet. Add a device to build a persistent wake inventory."
msgstr "尚未設定任何裝置。新增裝置以建立持久的喚醒清單。"

msgid "No probeable IPv4 address is currently known"
msgstr "目前沒有可探測的 IPv4 位址"

msgid "Offline"
msgstr "離線"

msgid "Online"
msgstr "線上"

msgid "Optional. Falls back to the default interface when present"
msgstr "可選。留空時會回退到預設介面。"

msgid "Optional. Used for shutdown and reachability checks"
msgstr "可選。用於關機與連通性檢查。"

msgid "Ping reachable with a known IPv4 address"
msgstr "具有已知 IPv4 且可被 Ping 到"

msgid "Refresh Status"
msgstr "重新整理狀態"

msgid "Refreshing device status"
msgstr "正在重新整理裝置狀態"

